query T multiline
EXPLAIN INDEX "mz_internal"."mz_cluster_deployment_lineage_ind";
----
mz_internal.mz_cluster_deployment_lineage_ind:
  →Arrange (#0{cluster_id})
    →Stream mz_internal.mz_cluster_deployment_lineage

mz_internal.mz_cluster_deployment_lineage:
  →With
    cte l0 =
      →Read mz_catalog.mz_audit_events
  →Return
    →With Mutually Recursive
      cte l1 =
        →Unarranged Raw Stream
          →Distinct GroupAggregate
            →Union
              →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                Project: #0, #0, #1
                Filter: like["u%"](#0{id})
                  →Arranged mz_catalog.mz_clusters
                    Key: (#0{id})
              →Stream l2
      cte l2 =
        →Map/Filter/Project
          Project: #3, #1, #2
            →Non-monotonic TopK
              Group By #0
              Order By #4 asc nulls_last
              Limit 1
              →Differential Cross Join %1:l0[×] » %0[×]
                after %0:
                  Project: #3..=#5, #1, #7
                  Filter: ((#5{cluster_name} = #2{cluster_name}) OR (#2{cluster_name} = (#5{cluster_name} || "_dbt_deploy"))) AND (#0{occurred_at} <= (#6{occurred_at} + 00:01:00)) AND (#0{occurred_at} >= (#6{occurred_at} - 00:01:00))
                  Map: abs(extract_epoch_iv((#6{occurred_at} - #0{occurred_at})))
                →Arrange (empty key)
                  →Non-monotonic TopK
                    Group By #0
                    Order By #3 desc nulls_first
                    Limit 1
                    →Differential Join %1:l0[#1{cluster_id}, #2{cluster_name}] » %0:l1[#0{cluster_id}, #2{cluster_name}]
                      →Arrange (#0{cluster_id}, #2{cluster_name})
                        →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                          Filter: (#0{cluster_id}) IS NOT NULL
                            →Arranged l1
                              Key: (#0..=#2)
                      →Arrange (#1{cluster_id}, #2{cluster_name})
                        →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                          Project: #3..=#5
                          Filter: (#0{event_type} != "drop") AND (#1{object_type} = "cluster") AND ((#0{event_type} = "create") OR ((#0{event_type} = "alter") AND (#2{details} ? "new_name"))) AND (#4) IS NOT NULL AND (#5) IS NOT NULL
                          TemporalFilter: mz_now() < timestamp_tz_to_mz_timestamp((#3{occurred_at} + 30 days))
                            →Read l0
                →Arrange (empty key)
                  →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                    Project: #3..=#5
                    Filter: (#0{event_type} = "drop") AND (#1{object_type} = "cluster")
                    TemporalFilter: mz_now() < timestamp_tz_to_mz_timestamp((#3{occurred_at} + 30 days))
                      →Read l0
    →Return
      →Stream l1

Source mz_catalog.mz_audit_events
  project=(#1..=#3, #5..=#7)
  filter=((#2{object_type} = "cluster") AND ((#1{event_type} = "drop") OR (#1{event_type} = "create") OR ((#1{event_type} = "alter") AND (#3{details} ? "new_name"))) AND (mz_now() < timestamp_tz_to_mz_timestamp((#5{occurred_at} + 30 days))))
  map=(coalesce((#3{details} ->> "id"), (#3{details} ->> "cluster_id")), coalesce((#3{details} ->> "name"), (#3{details} ->> "new_name")))

Used Indexes:
  - mz_catalog.mz_clusters_ind (*** full scan ***)

Target cluster: mz_catalog_server

EOF

