                  →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                    Project: #0
                      →Arranged mz_catalog.mz_indexes
                        Key: (#0{id})
            →Stream l2
      →Map/Filter/Project
        Project: #0, #1, #3
        Map: coalesce(#2{hydrated}, false)
          →Union
            →Map/Filter/Project
              Project: #0..=#2
              Map: null, null
                →Consolidating Union
                  →Negate Diffs
                    →Unarranged Raw Stream
                      →Distinct GroupAggregate
                        →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                          Project: #0
                            →Read l3
                  →Fused with Child Map/Filter/Project
                    Project: #0
                      →Arranged mz_catalog.mz_materialized_views
                        Key: (#0{id})
            →Stream l3
      →Map/Filter/Project
        Project: #0, #1, #3
